videos.description: With the clock winding down in the first quarter, Lashonda Monk lets it fly from three-quarter court and banks it home to beat the buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (ECU's Monk drains buzzer-beater from beyond half court) 2020/01/25

videos.headline: ECU's Monk drains buzzer-beater from beyond half court

videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield throws a perfect pass ahead to Christyn Williams, who gets hit as she drives to the rim, but contorts to make the shot anyway.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Williams absorbs contact for and-1 bucket) 2020/01/25

videos.headline: Williams absorbs contact for and-1 bucket
